\v 1 !Oteh-to! !Nolkeikei…ôn asoli ag…®n Tat…ô Uhg…®n t…ômolkeikei itah lan,\f + \fr 3:1  \ft Jon 3:16\f* m…ôm…ô t…ôtau…®n e tah m…ôm…ô nen…ôt…®n m…®n!\f + \fr 3:1  \ft Jon 1:12\f* K…ôni n…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn m…ôm…ô kitah …ôha. N…ôt…ômimi r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni k…ôsot…ôhruni…ôn m…ôm…ô kitah nen…ôt…®n m…®n,\f + \fr 3:1  \ft Jon 15:21; 16:2,3\f* m…ôt…ôu-inu ilah kot…ôruru Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 3:1  \ft Jon 15:21; 16:2,3\f*  
