\p
\v 16 Kitah kot…ôhrun vivi m…ôm…ô nolkeikei…ôn in tol lanu, m…ôt…ôu-inu Iesu t…ôm…ôfa r…ôhan n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn o tah.\f + \fr 3:16  \ft Jon 10:11\f* K…ôni t…ôhmen …ôm…ô lan…ôha, t…ôuv…®r m…ôm…ô kitah m…®n kot…ôf…ôn n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhatah o piatah m…®n.\f + \fr 3:16  \ft Jon 15:13; 1T…ôs 2:8\f*  
