\m
\v 1 N…®kik m…®n, n…ôm…ô i…ôt…ômimi k…ôti t…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô Narm…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g lan, matol in t…ôt…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm r…ôhan n…ôghati…ôn, k…ôni t…ôuv…®r p…®k m…ôm…ô on…ôkoteruh vivi motakil m…ôt…®g m…ôm…ô narm…®n …ôha t…ôtat…®g lan, in r…ôha Uhg…®n p…ôhri…ôn, u…ô s…ôni…ôm…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 4:1  \ft Jer 29:8\f* Kitah okot…ôkeikei moteh vivi m…ôt…ôu-inu i…ôni eiu…ô m…®n tep…ôt k…®nohiet r…ôk…®s m…ôut…ôghati e n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni.\f + \fr 4:1  \ft Mat 7:15; 1Jon 2:18\f*  
\v 2 Tol lan…ôha, it…ômah on…ôkot…ôhrun vivi m…ôm…ô in Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n i…ôt…ôm t…ôtat…®g e i…ôt…ômimi k…ôti, inu, Narm…®n i…ôt…ôm t…ôt…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kr…®sto i…ôt…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôni m…ôm…ô otahli=pa, k…ôni in t…ômuva e n…®p…ôt…®n,\f + \fr 4:2  \ft Jon 1:14; 1Jon 2:23\f* narm…®n …ôha in Narm…®n …ôhruahru r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 4:2  \ft Jon t…ôm…ôni tol lanu m…ôt…ôu-inu n…ôt…ômimi n…ôt…ôm k…ôm…ôutoht…ôu=p…ôn Nostisis…®m, n…ôg…ôtuni…ôn r…ôhalah t…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô Iesu, n…®p…ôt…®n p…ôhri…ôn t…®k…ô, m…ôt…ôu in narm…®n …ôm…ô, k…ôni in t…ômos narm…® i…ôt…ômi k…ôti. M…ôt…ôu n…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn, n…®p…ôt…®n …ôha ik…®n. N…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn, Iesu Kr…®sto in i…ôt…ômimi p…ôhri…ôn, k…ôni in m…®n Uhg…®n p…ôhri…ôn.\f*\f + \fr 4:2  \ft 1Kor 12:3\f*  
\v 3 M…ôt…ôu i…ôt…ômimi k…ôti i…ôt…ôm t…ôs…ôni p…ôt…®g…ômi…ôn m…ôm…ô Iesu in Kr…®sto i…ôt…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôni m…ôm…ô otahli=pa, narm…®n r…ôha i…ôt…ômimi …ôha, s…ôni…ôm…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n. In…ôha, in narm…®n r…ôha t…®k…®m…®r r…ôha Kr…®sto,\f + \fr 4:3  \ft 1Jon 2:22; 2Jon 1:7\f*\f + \fr 4:3  \ft E Ingl…®s, k…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô ‚Äúantichrist,‚Äù k…ôni n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô in t…®k…®m…®r r…ôha Kr…®sto.\f* i…ôt…ôm n…ômot…ôt…ôu r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô in ot…ôpanuva, k…ôni r…ôueiu t…®n…ôtat…®g r…ôk…®s e n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni.\f + \fr 4:3  \ft 1Jon 2:18\f*   
\p
\v 4 K…ôlk…ôl…ôh m…®n, it…ômah n…ôt…ômimi r…ôha Uhg…®n m…®n, k…ôni n…ômot…ôhgi r…ôk…®s i…ôni eiu…ô m…®n …ôha,\f + \fr 4:4  \ft Jon 16:33\f* m…ôt…ôu-inu Narm…®n i…ôt…ôm t…ôtat…®g e n…®kit…ômah in tapir…ôk…®s narm…®n i…ôt…ôm t…ôtat…®g e n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u.\f + \fr 4:4  \ft 2King 6:16; Rom 8:31\f*  
\v 5 Ilah n…ôt…ômimi r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u,\f + \fr 4:5  \ft Jon 15:19; 17:14,16\f* tol lan…ôha, n…ôghati…ôn m…®n r…ôhalah k…ôut…ôni, ilah r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni …ôm…ô, k…ôni n…ôt…ôm k…ôut…ôt…ôl…®g e lah, ilah m…®n n…ôt…ômi r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u.  
\v 6 M…ôt…ôu it…®mah r…ôha Uhg…®n. Tol lan…ôha, n…ôt…ômimi n…ôt…ôm kot…ôhrun Uhg…®n, ilah kot…ôt…ôl…®g e t…®mah. M…ôt…ôu n…ôt…ômimi n…ôt…ôm ilah s…ôni…ôm…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n, ilah k…ôsot…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn e t…ômah.\f + \fr 4:6  \ft Jon 8:47\f* K…ôni tol lan…ôha r…ôueiu, kitah okot…ôhrun …ôhruahru n…ôt…ômimi n…ôt…ôm Narm…®n r…ôha n…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn t…ôtat…®g e lah,\f + \fr 4:6  \ft Jon 14:17\f* m…®ne n…ôt…ômimi n…ôt…ôm narm…®n r…ôha neiu…ôi…ôn t…ôtat…®g e lah.\f + \fr 4:6  \ft Mak 13:5\f*   
\s1 Nolkeikei…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n m…®ne r…ôhatah  
\p
\v 7 N…®kik m…®n, p…ôh kitah kot…ôkeikei mautolkeikei itah m…®n,\f + \fr 4:7  \ft 1Jon 3:11\f* m…ôt…ôu-inu nolkeikei…ôn in tats…®p…ôn e Uhg…®n, k…ôni i…ôt…ôm tatol nolkeikei…ôn, in t…ômair vi m…®n muva nati Uhg…®n k…ôti,\f + \fr 4:7  \ft Jon 1:15\f* k…ôni t…ôhrun Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 4:7  \ft 1Jon 2:4\f*  
\v 8 M…ôt…ôu i…ôt…ômi u r…ôhan nolkeikei…ôn t…®k…ô, in t…ôruru Uhg…®n, m…ôt…ôu-inu Uhg…®n in n…ôuk…ôt…® nolkeikei…ôn.  
\v 9 Uhg…®n t…ômol …ôpu r…ôhan nolkeikei…ôn k…ôm tah lanu, m…ôm…ô in t…ômahli=pa N…ôt…®n n…ôuan k…ôti…ôh …ôm…ô,\f + \fr 4:9  \ft Jon 1:18\f* tuva e n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni, m…ôm…ô kitah okotos n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn ohni.\f + \fr 4:9  \ft Jon 3:16,17; 1Jon 5:11\f*  
\v 10 Nati u in nolkeikei…ôn p…ôhri…ôn, s…ôni…ôm…ô kitah k…ômotolkeikei Uhg…®n, m…ôt…ôu in t…ômolkeikei itah.\f + \fr 4:10  \ft Rom 5:8,10\f* Uhg…®n t…ômahli=pa N…ôt…®n tuva, k…ôni in t…ômol sakrifais aru e r…ôhan n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn o r…ôhatah noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n, m…ôm…ô ni…ôm…ôha ot…ôsol m…®ni…ôn Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 4:10  \ft Rom 3:25\f*   
\p
\v 11 Piak m…®n, Uhg…®n t…ômolkeikei p…®k itah lanu,\f + \fr 4:11  \ft Jon 3:16\f* k…ôni tol lanu lan, kitah m…®n okot…ôkeikei motol m…®n nolkeikei…ôn …ôha k…ôm tah m…®n.\f + \fr 4:11  \ft Jon 15:12; 1Jon 3:11\f*  
\v 12 I…ôt…ômi k…ôti t…ôsehi…ôn Uhg…®n nian k…ôti m…®ne.\f + \fr 4:12  \ft Jon 1:18\f* M…ôt…ôu n…ôm…ô kitah kotolkeikei itah m…®n, k…ôni Uhg…®n tat…®g e n…®kitah, k…ôni nolkeikei…ôn r…ôhan t…ômat…®g m…®npi vivi p…ôhri…ôn e n…®kitah.\f + \fr 4:12  \ft 1Jon 4:17; 2:5\f*   
\p
\v 13 Kitah kot…ôhrun\f + \fr 4:13  \ft 1Jon 2:3\f* m…ôm…ô kitah kotat…®g lan, k…ôni in t…ôtat…®g e tah, m…ôt…ôu-inu t…®n…ôfa r…ôk…®s r…ôhan Narm…®n k…ôm tah.\f + \fr 4:13  \ft 1Jon 3:24\f*  
\v 14 K…ôni it…®mah i…ômoteruh r…ôk…®s m…ôut…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm\f + \fr 4:14  \ft Jon 15:27\f* m…ôm…ô Tat…ô Uhg…®n in t…ômahli=pa N…ôt…®n m…ôm…ô in Iosmi…ôg…ôh r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni.\f + \fr 4:14  \ft Luk 2:11; Jon 3:17\f*  
\v 15 I…ôt…ômimi i…ôt…ôm t…ôt…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm m…ôm…ô Iesu in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, k…ôni Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g lan, k…ôni in m…®n t…ôtat…®g=p…ôn e Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 4:15  \ft 1Jon 3:24\f*  
\v 16 K…ôni tol lan…ôha, kitah kot…ôhrun nolkeikei…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n o tah, k…ôni m…ôutar…ôri…ô lan.  
\p Uhg…®n in nolkeikei…ôn.\f + \fr 4:16  \ft 1Jon 4:8\f* I…ôt…ômi t…ôtat…®g e nolkeikei…ôn, t…ôtat…®g=p…ôn e Uhg…®n, k…ôni Uhg…®n m…®n t…ôtat…®g lan.\f + \fr 4:16  \ft 1Jon 3:24\f*  
\v 17 Nian k…ôutat…®g lan…ôha e Uhg…®n, k…ôni nolkeikei…ôn r…ôhan t…ômat…®g m…®npi vivi p…ôhri…ôn e n…®kitah,\f + \fr 4:17  \ft 1Jon 4:12; 2:5\f* m…ôm…ô kitah k…ôsot…ôg…®ni…ôn\f + \fr 4:17  \ft Ef…ôs 3:12\f* e nian Uhg…®n otakil it…ômi, m…ôt…ôu-inu e n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u r…ôhatah noli…ôn t…ôhmen e Kr…®sto.  
\v 18 I…ôt…ômi u t…ôriau…ôh e nolkeikei…ôn, ko t…ôs…ôg…®ni…ôn e Uhg…®n. M…ôt…ôu-inu nolkeikei…ôn p…ôhri…ôn u, i…ôt…ôm t…®nat…ôu…ô r…ôk…®s e n…®kitah, t…ôt…ôhgi r…ôk…®s n…ôg…®ni…ôn.\f + \fr 4:18  \ft Rom 8:15\f* N…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn r…ôha nosi…ôn nalp…®ni…ôn tatol itah k…ôut…ôg…®n, k…ôni nati u t…ôt…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô r…ôhan nolkeikei…ôn p…ôhri…ôn t…ôs…ôu…ô …ôhan…ôhi…ôn e n…®kitah.   
\p
\v 19 Kitah kotolkeikei itah m…®n m…®ne Uhg…®n m…ôt…ôu-inu Uhg…®n t…ômaup…ôn molkeikei itah.  
\v 20 M…ôt…ôu n…ôm…ô i…ôt…ômi k…ôti t…ôni m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôu i…ôkolkeikei Uhg…®n,‚Äù m…ôt…ôu t…ôt…ôm…ôki …ôhan…ôh e pian u t…ôt…ôhat…ôt…ô m…®n e Kr…®sto,\f + \fr 4:20  \ft 1Jon 2:9\f* in ieiu…ô,\f + \fr 4:20  \ft 1Jon 1:6; 2:4\f* m…ôt…ôu-inu i…ôt…ômi t…ôsolkeikei…ôn pian u in tateh e n…ôhmt…®n,\f + \fr 4:20  \ft 1Jon 3:17\f* ko t…ôsolkeikei…ôn Uhg…®n, i…ôt…ôm in t…ôsehi…ôn.\f + \fr 4:20  \ft R…ôhatah noli…ôn t…ôt…ôg…ôtun …ôhruahru nati nak t…ôtat…®g e n…®kitah. N…ôm…ô i…ôt…ômimi k…ôti in tolkeikei p…®k Uhg…®n, nolkeikei…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n tat…®g e n…®kin, k…ôni ko in otolkeikei m…®n n…ôt…ômimi, k…ôni in otol noli…ôn t…ôuv…®r m…®n …ôm…ô k…ôm lah. M…ôt…ôu n…ôm…ô kitah k…ôsotolkeikei…ôn Uhg…®n, k…ôni ko kitah k…ôsotolkeikei…ôn m…®ni…ôn n…ôt…ômimi. K…ôni n…ôm…ô kitah k…ôsotolkeikei…ôn n…ôt…ômimi, t…ôt…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô k…ôsotolkeikei…ôn Uhg…®n\f*\f + \fr 4:20  \ft 1Jon 4:12; Jon 1:18\f*  
\v 21 K…ôni in t…ôm…ôfa r…ôhan n…ôghati…ôn k…ôm tah m…ôm…ô: i…ôt…ômimi p…ôh tolkeikei Uhg…®n in ot…ôkeikei molkeikei m…®n pian.\f + \fr 4:21  \ft 1Jon 2:7,9\f*   
\c 5  
\s1 Kitah kautol win m…ôt…ôu-inu kitah k…ôut…ôhat…ôt…ô e Iesu  
\m
\v 1 I…ôt…ômimi i…ôt…ôm t…ôt…ôhat…ôt…ô\f + \fr 5:1  \ft Jon 3:15\f* e Iesu m…ôm…ô in Kr…®sto i…ôt…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôni m…ôm…ô otahli=pa, i…ôt…ômi inu, in n…ôt…® Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 5:1  \ft Jon 1:13; 1Jon 2:22; 1Jon 2:23\f* k…ôni i…ôt…ômimi i…ôt…ôm in tolkeikei Tat…ô Uhg…®n, in tolkeikei m…®n nen…ôt…®n m…®n.\f + \fr 5:1  \ft 1Jon 2:23\f*  
\v 2 K…ôni n…ôm…ô kotolkeikei Uhg…®n k…ôni mautol n…ôuian,\f + \fr 5:2  \ft 1Jon 2:3\f* konu kitah kot…ôhrun m…ôm…ô kotolkeikei m…®n nen…ôt…®n m…®n.\f + \fr 5:2  \ft 1Jon 3:14\f*  
\v 3 M…ôt…ôu-inu n…ôm…ô kotolkeikei Uhg…®n, n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô, okotol n…ôuian.\f + \fr 5:3  \ft Jon 14:15\f* K…ôni r…ôhan n…ôghati…ôn ot…ôhmen e katip…ô i…ôt…ôm t…ôhvev…®g …ôm…ô.\f + \fr 5:3  \ft Mat 11:30\f*  
\v 4 N…ôt…ômi m…®n u ilah nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n m…®n,\f + \fr 5:4  \ft Jon 1:13\f* ilah kautol win e noli…ôn m…®n r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni. Konu n…ôhat…ôt…ôi…ôn r…ôhatah in t…ôt…ôfa n…ôsan…ôni…ôn o noli…ôn win e noli…ôn m…®n r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni.  
\v 5 ?P…ôh m…®n u ilah k…ôut…ôhtul …ôskas…®k motol win e noli…ôn m…®n r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u? Ilah …ôm…ô …ôha, n…ôt…ôm k…ôut…ôhat…ôt…ô m…ôm…ô Iesu in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n.   
\s1 I…ôru…ôsan k…®s…®l kahlol …ôpu Iesu Kr…®sto k…ôm tah  
\p
\v 6 Iesu Kr…®sto, in i…ôt…ômi u i…ôt…ôm t…ômuva, k…ôni n…ôhu m…®ne n…®ran\f + \fr 5:6  \ft Jon 19:34,35\f* katuol …ôpu in k…ôm tah m…ôm…ô in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n. S…ôni…ôm…ô n…ôhu …ôm…ô i…ôt…ôm tatol …ôpu in, m…ôt…ôu n…ôhu m…®ne n…®ran. Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n in t…ôt…ôru…ôsan n…ôghati…ôn mil u r…ôha n…ôhu m…®ne n…®r…ô, m…ôt…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm, k…ôni r…ôhan n…ôghati…ôn in n…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn m…ôt…ôu-inu Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n in n…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn.  
\v 7 K…ôni nuhapum…®ni…ôn k…®s…®l k…ôhl…ôru…ôsan ilahal m…®n.\f + \fr 5:7  \ft Jon 14:17\f*  
\v 8 Ilahal u, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, m…®ne n…ôhu, m…®ne n…®r…ô. K…ôni ilahal u, k…ôhleg…ôhan lan mahlol …ôpu n…ôghati…ôn r…ôhalahal m…®n.  
\v 9 Nian m…®n, kitah kaut…ôt…ôu n…ôghati…ôn m…®n i…ôt…ôm n…ôt…ômimi k…ôut…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm, m…ôut…ôhat…ôt…ô e lah.\f + \fr 5:9  \ft Jon 5:33,34\f* M…ôt…ôu nian Uhg…®n t…ôt…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm nati k…ôti, in iahgin tapir…ôk…®s, k…ôni kitah okot…ôhrun n…ôhat…ôt…ô t…ôhm…®n m…®n e r…ôhan n…ôghati…ôn, m…ôt…ôu-inu in Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 5:9  \ft Mat 3:16,17; Jon 5:32,37; 8:17,18\f* k…ôni in t…ôt…ôhtul p…ôt…®g…ôm o N…ôt…®n.   
\p
\v 10 I…ôt…ômimi i…ôt…ôm t…ôt…ôhat…ôt…ô e N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, in t…ôt…ôni n…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn e n…®kin o n…ôghati…ôn u r…ôha Uhg…®n. M…ôt…ôu i…ôt…ômimi i…ôt…ôm t…ôs…ôhat…ôt…ôi…ôn e n…ôghati…ôn u r…ôha Uhg…®n, t…ôhmen …ôm…ô m…ôm…ô in t…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n in ieiu…ô …ôm…ô,\f + \fr 5:10  \ft Jon 3:33; 1Jon 1:10\f* m…ôt…ôu-inu Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôhtul p…ôt…®g…ôm o N…ôt…®n, m…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm N…ôt…®n k…ôm in, m…ôt…ôu in t…ôs…ôni…ôn n…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn lan.  
\v 11 Konu n…ôghati…ôn i…ôt…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôni p…ôt…®g…ôm o N…ôt…®n, in tol lanu. Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôf…ôn n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn itul…®n\f + \fr 5:11  \ft Mat 25:46\f* k…ôm tah, konu n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn u, katos o N…ôt…®n.\f + \fr 5:11  \ft Jon 1:4\f*  
\v 12 I…ôt…ôm tatos N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, in tatos n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn. M…ôt…ôu i…ôt…ôm t…ôsosi…ôn N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, in t…ôsosi…ôn n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn.\f + \fr 5:12  \ft Jon 3:15,16,36\f*   
\s1 Naunun n…ôghati…ôn  
\p
\v 13 I…ôt…ôtei n…ôghati…ôn m…®n u k…ôm t…ômah n…ôt…ôm n…ôut…ôhat…ôt…ô e N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôhrun m…ôm…ô it…ômah n…ôkotos n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn itul…®n.\f + \fr 5:13  \ft 1Jon 5:11\f*  
\v 14 P…ôh k…ôsot…ôg…®ni…ôn,\f + \fr 5:14  \ft Ef…ôs 3:12; 1Jon 3:21\f* m…ôt…ôu kot…ôskas…®k o n…ôtapu…ôhi…ôn o nati k…ôti e n…ôhmt…® Uhg…®n. Nian okot…ôtapu…ôh o nati k…ôti k…ôm in i…ôt…ôm t…ôuv…®r e r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn, k…ôni kitah kot…ôhrun vivi m…ôm…ô in ot…ôt…ôu r…ôhatah n…ôfaki…ôn.\f + \fr 5:14  \ft Mat 7:7\f*  
\v 15 K…ôni n…ôm…ô kot…ôhrun m…ôm…ô in ot…ôt…ôu itah, k…ôni nati nak okoteasi…ô=p…ôn ohni, k…ôni k…®not…ôhrun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô okotos.\f + \fr 5:15  \ft 1King 3:12\f*   
\p
\v 16 N…ôm…ô koteh piatah k…ôti tatol noli…ôn t…ôrah, m…ôt…ôu s…ôni…ôm…ô noli…ôn t…ôrah i…ôt…ôm t…ôhrun niti-p…ôni…ôn e n…®m…®si…ôn, ik on…ôk…ôfaki ohni, k…ôni Uhg…®n ot…ôf…ôn n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn k…ôm i…ôt…ômi u.\f + \fr 5:16  \ft Jem 5:15\f* M…ôt…ôu noli…ôn t…ôrah k…ôti …ôha ik…®n i…ôt…ôm tatiti=p…ôn i…ôt…ômi e n…®m…®si…ôn,\f + \fr 5:16  \ft Hip 6:4-6; 10:26\f* k…ôni i…ôu i…ôs…ôni…ôn m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ôfaki o n…ôt…ômi m…®n i…ôt…ôm kautol noli…ôn …ôha.\f + \fr 5:16  \ft Jer 7:16; 14:11\f*\f + \fr 5:16  \ft E fes u, m…®ne fes 17, Jon t…ôt…ôghati e t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah i…ôt…ôm tatiti=p…ôn it…ômi e n…®m…®si…ôn. Jon t…ôt…ôghati e t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah i…ôt…ôm k…ôt…ôuhlin n…ômtaht…ômi o Kr…®sto. Noli…ôn t…ôrah …ôha, t…ôt…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô n…ôt…ômimi kautol ilah k…ôsotos…ôn n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn itul…®n, konu n…ôuvet…®n m…®n u m…ôm…ô narm…®lah t…®n…®m…®s. Nati u inu, Jon t…ôt…ôni …ôhag…ôhag k…ôm tah e 1Jon 5:12 m…®ne 1Jon 3:14. E Mat 12:31-32 kitah k…ôutafin n…ôuvet…®n m…®n e nol t…ôfag…ô u, n…ôni rahi…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.\f*  
\v 17 Noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n r…ôfin, ilah t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah,\f + \fr 5:17  \ft 1Jon 3:4\f* k…ôni m…ôt…ôu t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah m…®n …ôha ik…®n i…ôt…ôm k…ôsotiti-p…ôni…ôn i…ôt…ômi e n…®m…®si…ôn.\f + \fr 5:17  \ft 1Jon 5:16; 1Jon 2:1\f*   
\p
